divs: Sighting DetailsI went outside to the back of,my house to have a smoke with my wife and looked up to the sky to see the stars and a star just started moving pretty fast across the sky. I have been seeing this for quite sometime now not sure what they are but every now and again I see stars moving across the sky., as well as other things this has been going on for years now lately it's been more since I've moved to New Jersey from Miami
